\chapter{Development Environment}
\section{IDE}
Ecipse with the C/C++ plugin
\section{Version Control}
git with Github as server
\section{Nightly Build}
hudson for nifhtly Builds and test runs
\section{Graphics}
Gimp for all the graphics
\section{External Libraries}
SDL for all the rendering stuff
Box2D for the physics
yaml-cpp for the configfiles
cwiid for the wiimote input
\section{Operating system}
ArchLinux
\section{Compiler}
GCC 4.7.2
